    <briefdescription>
<para>32-bit Event Flag Group Synchronization. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides a bitmask event group mechanism for tasks and protothreads to set, clear, and wait on single or multiple event bit combinations (WAIT_ALL, WAIT_ANY, auto-clear). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
